text: Venray is a municipality in the Dutch province of Limburg. As of 2020, about 41,000 people were living in the municipality and about 28,500 people were living in the town. In 2010, parts of the former municipality of Meerlo- Wanssum were added to Venray (Blitterswijck, Geijsteren, and Wanssum). == References == == Other websites == * Plaatsengids Category:Settlements in Limburg (Netherlands) Category:Municipalities of Limburg (Netherlands)
